BYEON HO-IN
DIAGNOSIS: HEPATOCELLULAR CARCINOMA

202
00:17:20.789 --> 00:17:22.708
{\an8}<i>Dapat mong ihinto kaagad ang pag-inom.</i>

203
00:17:23.375 --> 00:17:24.752
Ang pagbabala ay medyo madilim.

204
00:17:26.086 --> 00:17:28.255
Nakausap mo na ba ang iyong pamilya tungkol dito?

205
00:17:34.386 --> 00:17:35.387
hindi pa.

206
00:17:42.061 --> 00:17:43.896
<i>Wala ka nang maraming oras na natitira.</i>

207
00:17:45.064 --> 00:17:46.648
