208
00:18:07.795 --> 00:18:09.755
BANG EUN-MI

209
00:18:20.933 --> 00:18:22.309
Ang bagay tungkol sa pagkain ay...

210
00:18:25.145 --> 00:18:27.022
na kung kumain ka ng marami, mabusog ka.

211
00:18:28.315 --> 00:18:30.692
Sa alkohol,
kung uminom ka ng marami, malasing ka.

212
00:18:35.405 --> 00:18:36.698
Lahat ng bagay ay may hangganan.

213
00:18:38.408 --> 00:18:39.535
Pero

214
00:18:40.702 --> 00:18:42.204
